snippet: The Unocal Corporation, which traces its history to the beginning of California's oil industry, said yesterday that it had reached a preliminary agreement to sell its crude oil and natural gas assets in the state for more than $500 million....
lead_paragraph: The Unocal Corporation, which traces its history to the beginning of California's oil industry, said yesterday that it had reached a preliminary agreement to sell its crude oil and natural gas assets in the state for more than $500 million.

headline.main: UNOCAL FINDS BUYER FOR OIL AND GAS ASSETS
